      • verifyFillInExceptions

        private long[] verifyFillInExceptions(SegmentedTimeline timeline,
                            java.lang.String[] exceptionString,
                            java.text.Format fmt)
                               throws java.text.ParseException
        Adds an array of exceptions to the timeline. The timeline exception list is first cleared.
        Parameters:
        timeline - The timeline where the exceptions will be stored
        exceptionString - The exceptions to load
        fmt - The date formatter to use to parse each exceptions[i] value

        Throws:
        java.text.ParseException - If there is any exception parsing each exceptions[i] value.
